address.descriptionText: Contact information for a page or article element

area.descriptionText: Hyperlink or dead area on an image map

base.descriptionText: Base URL and default target navigable for hyperlinks and forms

blockquote.descriptionText: A section quoted from another source

br.descriptionText: Line break, e.g. in poem or postal address

colgroup.descriptionText: Group of columns in a table

datalist.descriptionText: Container for options for combo box control

div.descriptionText: Generic flow container, or container for name-value groups in dl elements

dl.descriptionText: Association list consisting of zero or more name-value groups

footer.descriptionText: Footer for a page or section

header.descriptionText: Introductory or navigational aids for a page or section

main.descriptionText: Container for the dominant contents of the document

optgroup.descriptionText: Group of options in a list box

option.descriptionText: Option in a list box or combo box control

source.descriptionText: Image source for img or media source for video or audio

tbody.descriptionText: Group of rows in a table

tfoot.descriptionText: Group of footer rows in a table

thead.descriptionText: Group of heading rows in a table

time.descriptionText: Machine-readable equivalent of date- or time-related data
